{
  "info": {
    "name": "BlockTrade Backend - Complete Auth & LC API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for BlockTrade Authentication and Letter of Credit system. This collection provides comprehensive testing for all authentication flows and LC operations to help frontend developers integrate the APIs.\n\n## ðŸ” Authentication Flow:\n1. **Register** - Create new user account\n2. **Login** - Get access and refresh tokens\n3. **Use Protected Endpoints** - Include Bearer token in Authorization header\n4. **Refresh Token** - Get new access token when expired\n\n## ðŸ“‹ Available Modules:\n- **Authentication**: Register, Login, Profile Management, Password Management\n- **Letter of Credit**: Create, View, Update, Search, Status Management\n- **User Management**: Admin functions (Coming Soon)\n\n## ðŸš€ Getting Started:\n1. Set your `base_url` environment variable (default: http://localhost:3000)\n2. Run the Login request to get your access token\n3. The token will be automatically saved and used for subsequent requests\n\n## ðŸ¦ Test Users:\n- **Bank Admin**: admin@globalbank.com / SecurePass123!\n- **Bank Officer**: officer@globalbank.com / SecurePass123!\n- **Corporate User**: corporate@tradecorp.com / SecurePass123!\n\n## âš™ï¸ Environment Variables:\n- `base_url`: API base URL\n- `access_token`: JWT access token (auto-set)\n- `refresh_token`: JWT refresh token (auto-set)\n- `user_id`: Current user ID (auto-set)\n- `organization_id`: Current organization ID (auto-set)",
